2011 U.S. EPA Presidential Green Chemistry Challenge Award[30]
2011 ICIS Best Business Innovation Award[31]
2012 Biotech Canada Gold Leaf Award - Early Stage Company of the Year: Industrial & Agricultural[32]
2013 4.5 Stars Environmental Leader[33]

